Every backend now follows the same pattern: **create provider client → build agent → call `agent.prompt()`**. Adding OpenAI or Claude is a 3-line addition to `ChatAgentSpec` — just add a variant, parse arm, and `build()` arm calling `openai::Client` / `anthropic::Client` the same way.

