                        "  [{:2}] {} — {}{}",
                        i + 1,
                        p.title,
                        p.format_authors(),
                        p.format_year()
                    );
                    let url = p.best_pdf_url();
                    if !url.is_empty() {
                        println!("       /download {}", url);
                    }
                }
                self.last_search_results = papers;
                println!("\nUse /download <url> to ingest any paper.");
            }
            Err(e) => println!("arXiv search error: {}", e),
        }
